    Author:
    Thomas Taschner Taken from http://stackoverflow.com/questions/8370290/generating-pi-to-nth-digit-java, made some slight changes so it fits to our interface. This class calculates the decimal places of PI with arbitrary precision. The used algorithm is hard to understand and explain so I won't even bother doing that.
